<text top="109" left="122" width="327" height="14" font="1">This statement will be issued as a document of the</text>
<text top="127" left="90" width="325" height="14" font="1">Security Council under the symbol S/PRST/1998/14.</text>
<text top="163" left="122" width="327" height="14" font="1">The Security Council has thus concluded the present</text>
<text top="181" left="90" width="358" height="14" font="1">stage of its consideration of the item on its agenda. The</text>
<text top="199" left="90" width="308" height="14" font="1">Security Council will remain seized of the matter.</text>
<text top="236" left="122" width="192" height="14" font="5"><i>The meeting rose at 11.30 a.m.</i></text>
